1	INTRODUCTION AND DEFINITIONS
1.1 These Member Terms (including our BLU Privacy Policy) govern the collection and use of BLU Points, the membership of the BLU Points Program and the use of BLU’s website and Mobile Application. These Terms may be changed or updated occasionally to meet the requirements and standards. Therefore Members are encouraged to frequently visit these sections in order to be updated about the changes made to these Terms. Modifications will be effective on the day they are posted.
1.2	For the purpose of these Member Terms, the following terms shall have the following meaning:
1.2.1	Member Terms – the terms set out herein;
1.2.2	Member – means the person who is a member of the BLU Points Program and whose name is registered against the Membership Number;
1.2.3	Program Partner – means any business participating in the BLU Points Program to offer BLU Points or Rewards to Members
1.2.4	BLU Points Program – means the loyalty program operated by us pursuant to which Members earn BLU Points from Program Partners and spend them on Rewards;
1.2.5	Membership Number – means the membership number allocated to a Member in accordance with these Member Terms;
1.2.6	BLU Points – means the common loyalty currency issued and redeemed by Program Partners across the BLU Points Program;
1.2.7	BLU Account – an account number that is set up under one Membership Number and which is used by Member within the BLU Points Program to earn and redeem points;
1.2.8	BLU Card – means, where issued, a Membership card;
1.2.9	Reward(s) – goods or services supplied, by or on behalf of us, upon redemption by a Member of an appropriate number of BLU Points or, where permitted, a combination of cash and BLU Points;
1.2.10	Coupon – a digital number obtained through a redemption process and used to redeem for a specific goods or services at Program Partners or Suppliers;
1.2.11	PIN Code –a four-digit number sent to Member at the time of enrollment and used for redemption purposes
1.2.12	BLU, we, us, our – mean BLU Solutions Limited, a company established in the British Virgin Islands, having its address at c/o CCS Trustees Limited, 265 Main Street, Road Town, Tortola, British Virgin Islands; and
1.2.13	Website and Mobile application – mean the pages and the screens applicable to the BLU Points Program available at www.blupoints.com and on the iOS and Android app stores.
2	MEMBERSHIP ENROLLMENT
2.1	A Member can enroll in the BLU Points Program by registering online at www.blupoints.com, through the BLU mobile application available on the Apple and Android mobile application stores or at businesses participating in the BLU Points Program (“Program Partners”). Once registered, Member can start earning BLU Points across the program network;
2.2	Member may be issued a BLU Card, which the Member can use to identify him/herself to the Program Partner to earn or redeem BLU Points or to avail of any service offered to Members;
2.3	We will set up a BLU Account to record BLU Points earned or redeemed by the Member. Points can only be redeemed once the BLU Account is activated by using the PIN at Program Partner locations or by entering it online on the Website;
2.4	A Member by registering and becoming a Member in the BLU Points Program agrees to receive marketing information from us or be contacted by us for promotional purposes in connection with the BLU Points Program and/or by participating companies;
3	POINTS COLLECTION
3.1	BLU has Program Partners through whom Member earns BLU Points. We award Points when one of our Program Partners tells us a Member has undertaken a relevant transaction with them. (“Suppliers”) are companies with whom a Member can redeem BLU Points to obtain Rewards. These participating companies may change - an up to date list of Program Partners and Suppliers is available from us at any time. Program Partners determine the particular transactions on which BLU Points can be earned and the number of BLU Points to be earned. There is a set number of BLU Points needed to obtain a Reward. Each of these will change but in most cases there will be a base offer with further bonus offers that come and go. We cannot control every specific change in the participating companies or their offers but we will ensure that while BLU is in operation a range of offers is available;
3.2 BLU Points are earned for purchases with any other Program Partner if a Member presents his/her BLU Card or the Membership Number or other required information before entering into a transaction on which such other Program Partner offers BLU Points;
3.3	BLU Points cannot be redeemed until credited to a BLU Account. Program Partners will take different periods to notify us of BLU Points to be credited. We are not responsible for a failure, delay or error by a Program Partner notifying us of BLU Points to be credited;
3.4	BLU Points can be transferred to another BLU Account. The transfer will be subject to a transfer fee equivalent to 5% of the amount of the points transferred or 100 (one hundred) BLU Points, whichever is greater;
3.5	BLU Points can only be earned, held, transferred or redeemed as set out in these Member Terms. Any other use, award, sale, exchange or transfer of BLU Points, or attempt to do so, is a serious breach of these Member Terms. Any BLU Points not earned and held in accordance with these Member Terms will be invalid and cannot be redeemed for Rewards. Any such BLU Points on a BLU Account will be deducted and, if they are redeemed, we will ask the Supplier to cancel the relevant Rewards and we may take other appropriate action. BLU Points have no cash value;
3.6	A Member who continues to collect will get a regular update of the BLU Points position as we know it on the date we issue the update in respect of his/her BLU Account including the BLU Points collected and redeemed by such Member on such BLU Account. Account information is also available from us and can be accessed on the Website or through the Mobile Application. We will correct a BLU Account if it is shown to our reasonable satisfaction to be wrong but, unless there are clear records showing this, our decision is final;
3.7	BLU reserves the right to reverse the BLU points credit issued by any partner, who discontinues operating within BLU for any reason;
4	REDEMPTION AND REWARDS
4.1	All Rewards are subject to availability and stocks may be limited. Transactions on which BLU Points are earned or redeemed are made directly with the relevant Program Partner or Supplier and we have no responsibility for the delivery, standard, quality or otherwise of any goods and services received or supplied or the failure of a Supplier to honor a redemption or make a specific Reward available. These transactions and all Rewards are subject to all applicable legal terms and the terms and conditions (including booking requirements, cancellation restrictions, return conditions, warranties and limitations of liability) of the Program Partner or Supplier. When BLU Points are redeemed we may act as intermediary between the relevant Member and the Supplier and/or Program Partner and we will do what we can to ensure such Rewards are supplied by the relevant Supplier and/or Program Partner;
4.2	The number of BLU Points required to redeem any Reward found on the Website or at a Program Partner location may change without prior notice;
4.3	At the time of requesting the reward, Member’s current BLU Points balance must be at least equal to the total BLU Points value that the Reward Member is requesting. Reward offers cannot be used in conjunction with any other Reward Supplier offers unless otherwise stated;
4.4	Once a Reward has been delivered or picked up, it cannot be returned or exchanged for BLU Points or other Rewards;
4.5	If a product is out of stock, BLU will suggest a replacement and it is the Member’s decision to accept or refuse the replacement. Where a replacement is not taken then the BLU Points will be credited back into Member’s account within 10 working days after notifying us;
4.6	If the Reward is faulty, the Supplier’s warranty will apply and the Member must revert to the Supplier for support and assistance;
4.7	Some Rewards may differ slightly from the image shown on the Website and on the Mobile Application;
4.8	Rewards (excluding Coupons) which are not claimed within six months after the date of redemption, will expire if the Member is not reachable;
4.9	Rewards will be delivered directly by the Supplier within ten working days;
4.10	To redeem his/her BLU Points in-store at Program Partners’ locations, the Member must use his/her PIN Code;
5	COUPONS
5.1	Coupons are issued by BLU for use at the specified Supplier and for the specified Reward. They must be indicated at the time of purchase for the Reward to be delivered;
5.2	Coupons can only be used once and have a validity of 6 months and are not valid beyond the expiry date indicated on the Coupon. If the specific Reward is out of stock and Member decided not to take a replacement, the Coupon can be cancelled at any time within the 6 months validity period. If Member redeems Coupon for an item of higher value than the original specific Reward, Member may wish to pay the excess value in cash but acceptance will be up to the Program Partner’s discretion. On the other hand, if Coupons are redeemed against an item of lesser value than the original specific reward, no change will be given;
5.3	Coupons cannot be exchanged for cash, sold or transferred for value. They remain the property of BLU. The Rewards redeemed with Coupons are the responsibility of the rewards provider and not BLU;
5.4	For Coupons cancellations and refunds please contact the local BLU Call Center during working hours or send BLU an email at info@blupoints.com. A cancellation fee of 2.5% in BLU Points equivalent of the total Coupon value or 300 BLU Points, whichever is greater will be applied. BLU Points will be credited back to the members account within 10 days following receipt of the cancellation fee and returned vouchers. For Coupons purchased with BLU Points that have subsequently expired, the expired BLU Points will be forfeited and not credited back to the members account;
5.5	For lost Coupons, Member should contact the local BLU Call Center or send an email to info@blupoints.com. Coupons will be re-issued or refunded within 10 working days;
