6.1	BLU and/or Supplier are not responsible for the unauthorized use of Coupons. Supplier terms and conditions also apply on the use of Coupons or on the delivery of the Reward;
6.2	We cannot be held liable for any loss, theft, damage or unauthorized use of a BLU Card, Member’s PIN Code, or Reward, whether in the course of delivery or otherwise. Any replacement of a BLU Card can be provided at the discretion of the Program Partner;
6.3	All conditions and warranties, whether expressed or implied and whether arising under legislation or otherwise, as to the condition, suitability, quality, fitness or safety of any Reward supplied are expressly excluded to the full extent permitted by law. Any liability that cannot be fully excluded is limited, where permitted, to replacing, repairing or crediting the value of the Reward at our discretion;
6.4	A Member must enter his/her personal PIN Code when conducting a redemption transaction in the BLU Points Program. Additional security questions might be asked by the Program Partner or a BLU staff. All Rewards redeemed on a BLU Account which are sent by post will be sent to the latest address we have for the Member or the address provided at the time of checkout;
6.5	It is the Member’s responsibility to ensure the PIN Code is not compromised, shared with anyone, or mishandled. Any loss resulting from the unauthorized use of the Member’s PIN code is the Member’s responsibility alone;
7	OTHER GENERAL TERMS
7.1	BLU Points have a three-year expiry date. They will be lost if expired. Additionally, they will be lost if the relevant BLU Account is closed or the BLU Points Program ends. Where BLU Points are redeemed for a Coupon carrying a specified cash discount or benefit, the Coupon will have an expiry date specified on it and will be subject to any other terms and conditions stated on the Coupon or otherwise publicized;
7.2	Redeemed BLU Points cannot be used again. If a transaction on which BLU Points are issued or redeemed is cancelled, reversed or not completed, we will reverse the associated BLU Points movement when instructed by the relevant Program Partner or Supplier. If insufficient BLU Points are available, or we suspect fraud or misconduct, Rewards may be refused or cancelled;
7.3	Our Privacy Policy (which is part of these Member Terms) sets out the information that we will gather on Members and how a Member uses his/her BLU Card or BLU Account and earns and redeems BLU Points, how this information will be used and whom it may be shared with. We will comply with our Privacy Statement – every Member should read it carefully;
7.4	BLU Cards are our property and must be returned to us on request or destroyed when no longer valid for use. The Member is responsible for the security of all BLU Cards issued on his/her BLU Account and all Coupons issued on that account. If a BLU Card or a PIN code is lost or the holder thinks an unauthorized person has become aware of any security code, password or account number, they should contact the BLU Call Center immediately and/or change the PIN through the Website or Mobile Application. Coupons should be treated like cash. We cannot be responsible for any unauthorized use of BLU Points or any lost or stolen Coupons;
7.5	We may close any BLU Account on which no BLU Points have been earned or redeemed for a continuous period of at least 12 months. We may also, on notifying the Member, immediately suspend or terminate the rights of any Member and/or close any relevant BLU Account, if they breach these Member Terms, if we reasonably believe that they have dealt with BLU Points in a manner not permitted by these Member Terms or any applicable Program Partner's terms and conditions, if there is any theft from or misconduct in connection with us, any Program Partner or Supplier, if they supply false or misleading information to us or if they are abusive or offensive to any member of our staff. A Member can close his/her BLU Account at any time by notifying us. If a BLU Account is closed Member’s rights to redeem BLU Points from that BLU Account are lost;
7.6	We may make changes to these Member Terms and will give the Member as much notice as we reasonably can. Earning or redeeming BLU Points on a BLU Account will constitute acceptance of the revised Member Terms. We may suspend or terminate the BLU Points Program but will give as much notice as we reasonably can before we do so. If this happens all BLU Accounts will be suspended or terminated. If we sell or transfer BLU to another company we may transfer all of our rights and obligations under these Member Terms without any further consent and may disclose or transfer all information we hold about Members to a prospective or actual new owner. Such a disclosure or transfer will not alter the rights of such Members in respect of the use that can be made of such information by such other company;
